	* src/include/PT/Stitcher.h: const fixes

2004-06-10 19:26  dangelo

	* src/: hugin/CPImageCtrl.cpp, hugin/ImageCenter.cpp,
	  hugin/ImageOrientationPanel.cpp, hugin/ImagesPanel.cpp,
	  hugin/Makefile, hugin/MyProgressDialog.cpp,
	  hugin/PreviewPanel.cpp, hugin/RunOptimizerFrame.cpp,
